r%20%26quot%3Bholding%20on%20for%20dear%20life%26quot%3B%20and%20resist%20the%20urge%20to%20sell%20your%20positions%2C%20this%20can%20prove%20to%20be%20an%20imprudent%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake%20the%20story%20of%20Glauber%20Contessoto%2C%20for%20example.%20The%2037-year-old%20crypto%20trader%20became%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdogecoin-millionaire-explains-why-recent-drop-does-not-shake-bullishness-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDogecoin%20millionaire%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202021%20after%20his%20initial%20%24250%2C000%20investment%20in%20Dogecoin%20ballooned%20in%20just%20three%20months.%20Then%20things%20turned%20south.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20the%20very%20top%2C%20my%20Dogecoin%20was%20worth%20%243%20million.%20And%20then%20after%20that%2C%20the%20bear%20market%20came%2C%20and%20crypto%20in%20general%20dipped%20down%2C%26quot%3B%20Contesso%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20an%20interview.%20%26quot%3BI%20saw%20my%20portfolio%20go%20from%20%243%20million%20all%20the%20way%20back%20down%20to%20about%20%24200%2C000.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20crypto%20assets%20enjoying%20another%20rally%2C%20Contessoto%20says%20he%20plans%20to%20approach%20things%20differently%20this%20time%2C%20taking%20profits%20earlier%20and%20diversifying.%20These%20are%20common%20strategies%20for%20investors%20to%20lock%20in%20gains%20and%20reduce%20the%20risk%20of%20losing%20their%20money%20if%20prices%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20some%20ways%20experts%20recommend%20reducing%20risks%20after%20a%20big%20run-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2252c55e46-eb33-4f72-a869-d96c9bd3d248%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EProfit-taking%20strategies%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EFirst%2C%20have%20a%20plan%20for%20getting%20out%20of%20an%20asset.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20important%20to%20have%20an%20exit%20strategy%20to%20minimize%20potential%20losses%2C%20especially%20with%20a%20risky%20asset%20class%20such%20as%20cryptocurrency.%20Accordin