0the%20YSR%20Congress%20Party%20has%20said%20that%20the%20deal%20was%20between%20government%20agencies%20and%20no%20private%20parties%2C%20including%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%20were%20involved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20a%20press%20conference%20on%20Thursday%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said%20the%20Solar%20Energy%20Corporation%20of%20India%20(SECI)%2C%20%C2%A0which%20is%20a%20central%20government-run%20public%20sector%20unit%20made%20an%20offer%20for%20power%20to%20several%20states%2C%20including%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Odisha%2C%20at%20Rs%202.49%20per%20unit.%20Pointing%20out%20that%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20had%20never%20bought%20power%20at%20a%20cheaper%20rate%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20said%20that%20other%20incentives%20were%20also%20offered%20to%20the%20state%2C%20including%20some%20waivers%2C%20which%20would%20have%20saved%20the%20government%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20YSRCP%20chief%20emphasised%20that%20the%20contract%20was%20between%20SECI%2C%20the%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20government%20and%20the%20state%20power%20distribution%20company%20and%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20any%20other%20agency%20intervening.%20He%20said%20that%20some%20media%20houses%20with%20political%20motives%20are%20putting%20out%20names%20suggesting%20bribery%20and%20that%20he%20would%20sue%20Eenadu%20and%20Andhra%20Jyothy%2C%20which%20he%20described%20as%20controlled%20by%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20TDP%20chief%20Chandrababu%20Naidu%2C%20for%20Rs%20100%20crore.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Reddy%20said%20no%20bribery%20was%20involved%20and%2C%20responding%20to%20a%20question%20on%20whether%20Mr%20Naidu%20could%20cancel%20the%20deal%2C%20the%20former%20chief%20minister%20said%20it%20would%20not%20be%20wise%20to%20do%20so.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20his%20meetings%20with%20Adani%20Group%20Chairman%20Gautam%20Adani%2C%20Mr%20Reddy%20said%20Mr%20Adani%20has%20several%20ongoing%20projects%20in%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20it%20is%20never%20unusual%20for%20the%20head%20of%20a%20state%20to%20be%20meeting%20with%20industry%20leaders.%20He%20said%20the%20meetings%20are%20intended%20to%20build%20a%20relationship%20of%20confidence%20and%20trust.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20the%20BJD%20and%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20had%20also%20rejected%20the%20allegations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20former%20Energy%20Minister%20of%20Odisha%2C%20Pratap%20Keshari%20Deb%2C%20had%20said%20that%20the%20agreement%20was%20to%20procure%20500%20MW%20of%20renewable%20energy%20from%20the%20SECI%20at%20the%20lowest%20rates%20discovered%20by%20the%20PSU.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20engagement%20with%20any%20private%20party%20whatsoever%2C%20including%20the%20Adani%20Group%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said%20earlier%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETamil%20Nadu%20Electricity%20Minister%20V%20Senthil%20Balaji%20said%20the%20state%20has%20an%20understanding%20to%20buy%20power%20only%20from%20a%20firm%20owned%20by%20the%20Union%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20like%20to%20first%20clarify%20that%20as%20regards%20TN%20Generation%20and%20Distribution%20Corporation%20(TANGEDCO)%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20kind%20of%20commercial%20relationship%20with%20Mr%20Adani's%20company%20during%20the%20past%20three%20years%20(after%20the%20DMK%20formed%20the%20government%20in%20May%202021)%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Balaji%20had%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Fully%20Compliant'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Adani%20Group%20has%20firmly%20denied%20a%20US%20government%20department%20report%20alleging%20bribery%20for%20power%20contracts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20possible%20legal%20recourse%20will%20be%20sought.%20The%20Adani%20Group%20has%20always%20upheld%20and%20is%20steadfastly%20committed%20to%20maintaining%20the%20highest%20standards%20of%20governance%2C%20transparency%20and%20regulatory%20compliance%20across%20all%20jurisdictions%20of%20its%20operations.%20We%20assure%20our%20stakeholders%2C%20partners%20and%20employees%20that%20we%20are%20a%20law-abiding%20organisation%2C%20fully%20compliant%20with%20all%20laws%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Group%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20lawyer%20and%20former%20Attorney%20General%20of%20India%20Mukul%20Rohatgi%20has%20also%20punched%20holes%20in%20the%20allegations%20against%20the%20Adani%20Group%20and%20said%20Mr%20Adani%20and%20his%20nephew%20Sagar%20Adani%20have%20not%20been%20accused%20of%20bribery%20or%20obstructing%20justice%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Disclaimer%3A%20New%20Delhi%20Television%20is%20a%20subsidiary%20of%20AMG%20Media%20Networks%20Limited%2C%20an%20Adani%20Group%20Company.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732799160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-12%2F7mhanj8k_jagan-reddy-650_625x300_31_December_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-andhra-chief-minister-jagan-reddy-rejects-charges-on-adani-says-power-deal-was-between-two-government-agencies-7126544%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%20and%20the%20Biju%20Janata%20Dal%20(BJD)%20in%20Odisha%2C%20former%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Jagan%20Reddy%20has%20rejected%20US%20charges%20that%20government%20officials%20took%20bribes%20for%20a%20power%20purchase%20agreement.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fex-andhra-chief-minister-jagan-reddy-rejects-charges-on-adani-says-power-deal-was-between-two-government-agencies-7126544%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Air%20India%20transformation%20is%20Test%20match%2C%20not%20T20%3B%20more%20work%20to%20do%3A%20Campbell%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732798846000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fair-i