0on%20targeting%20domestic%20firms%20supplying%20manufacturing%20equipment%20to%20chipmakers.%20The%20suggested%20curbs%20would%20add%20an%20extra%20100%20Chinese%20chip%20equipment%20makers%20to%20the%20entity%20list%2C%20the%20outlet%20reported.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20pushed%20the%20share%20price%20of%20ASML%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Dutch%20firm%20supplying%20crucial%20specialized%20equipment%20to%20chip%20manufacturers%2C%20including%20China's%20SMIC%20%E2%80%94%20up%20by%20more%20than%204.27%25%20Thursday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETokyo%20Electron%2C%20which%20also%20sells%20equipment%20for%20manufacturing%20chips%2C%20saw%20its%20share%20price%20climb%20by%20more%20than%206%25%20on%20Thursday.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20restrictions%2C%20expected%20as%20soon%20as%20next%20week%2C%20could%20also%20add%20chip%20makers%20to%20the%20sanctions%20list%2C%20including%20key%20suppliers%20to%20Chinese%20smartphone%20maker%20Huawei%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bloomberg.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2F2024-11-28%2Fus-readies-china-chip-curbs-that-stop-short-of-earlier-proposals%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBloomberg%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.wired.com%2Fstory%2Fmemory-restrictions-china-advanced-chips%2F%3F_sp%3Db9fea288-3156-4965-ae78-33cc9eedc97b.1732753802630%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWired%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%2C%20citing%20people%20familiar%20with%20the%20matter.%20The%20new%20proposals%20would%20affect%20fewer%20Huawei%20suppliers%2C%20the%20reports%20added.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20part%20of%20the%20sweeping%20sanctions%2C%20the%20US%20could%20add%20200%20Chinese%20chip%20firms%20to%20its%20trade%20blacklist%2C%20Wired%20reported.%20The%20controls%20could%20also%20include%20restrictions%20around%20trading%20memory%20chips%2C%20which%20are%20crucial%20for%20the%20development%20of%20AI%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22469c2cbe-52b9-4f06-8b0b-54a21655a9e5%5C%22%3E'Malicious%20attempts%20to%20block%20and%20su