e%20clarified%20that%20US%20aid%20to%20Ukraine%20will%20not%20be%20dependent%20on%20whether%20the%20conscription%20age%20is%20lowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20absolutely%20going%20to%20keep%20sending%20Ukraine%20weapons%20and%20equipment.%20We%20know%20that's%20vital.%20But%20so%2C%20too%2C%20is%20manpower%20at%20this%20point%2C%26quot%3B%20National%20Security%20Council%20spokesman%20John%20Kirby%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.france24.com%2Fen%2Flive-news%2F20241128-us-tells-ukraine-to-lower-conscription-age-to-18%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAFP%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20fact%2C%20we%20believe%20manpower%20is%20the%20most%20vital%20need%20they%20have.%20So%2C%20we're%20also%20ready%20to%20ramp%20up%20our%20training%20capacity%20if%20they%20take%20appropriate%20steps%20to%20fill%20out%20their%20ranks%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Kirby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20months%20he%20has%20left%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-atacms-permission-ukraine-russia-too-late-make-huge-difference-2024-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBiden%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20been%20scrambling%20to%20push%20measures%20to%20aid%20the%20war%20effort%20in%20Ukraine.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20said%20earlier%20this%20month%20that%20Biden%20%26quot%3Bhas%20committed%20to%20making%20sure%20that%20every%20dollar%20we%20have%20at%20our%20disposal%20will%20be%20pushed%20out%20the%20door%26quot%3B%20before%20Trump's%20inauguration%20in%20January.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20by%20BI%20for%20comment.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-tells-ukraine-cut-conscription-age-18-fix-lack-manpower-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732798068000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F674860c2ede4eeae392a3c98%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-tells-ukraine-cut-conscription-age-18-fix-lack-manpower-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20current%20minimum%20conscription%20age%20is%2025.%20The%20US%20thinks%20reducing%20it%20will%20help%20Ukraine%20keep%20up%20with%20Russia's%20military.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22habraham%40insider.com%20(Hannah%20Abraham)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-tells-ukraine-cut-conscription-age-18-fix-lack-manpower-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Court%20Order%20On%20Ajmer%20Dargah%20Sparks%20Intense%20Political%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fafter-mathura-varanasi-claims-of-temple-under-ajmer-dargah-court-issues-notice-7120340%5C%22%3EAjmer%20court's%20decision%20to%20hear%20a%20petition%3C%2Fa%3E%20claiming%20the%20presence%20of%20a%20Shiva%20temple%20under%20the%20Ajmer%20dargah%2C%20has%20sparked%20intense%20political%20debate%2C%20coming%20as%20it%20does%20after%20similar%20claims%20over%20mosques%20and%20dargahs%20in%20Mathura%2C%20Varanasi%20and%20Dhar.%20Amid%20intense%20criticism%20of%20Opposition%20leaders%20--%20who%20pointed%20out%20that%20days%20ago%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20has%20sent%20a%20chador%20to%20the%20Ajmer%20dargah%20--%20leaders%20of%20the%20BJP%20have%20claimed%20a%20decision%20to%20check%20out%20the%20presence%20of%20temples%20under%20such%20disputed%20structures%20is%20fair.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20court%20has%20ordered%20survey%20in%20Ajmer.%20What%20is%20the%20problem%20if%20court%20has%20ordered%20a%20survey%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Union%20minister%20Giriraj%20Singh.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20truth%20that%20when%20Mughals%20came%20to%20India%2C%20they%20demolished%20our%20temples.%20The%20Congress%20government%20has%20only%20done%20appeasement%20till%20now.%20If%20(Jawaharlal)%20Nehru%20would%20have%20stopped%20it%20in%201947%20itself%2C%20there%20would%20have%20been%20no%20need%20to%20approach%20the%20court%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20argument%20is%20a%20law%20made%20in%201991%2C%20that%20maintains%20that%20barring%20Ayodhya%2C%20status%20quo%20as%20on%20August%2015%2C%201947%2C%20will%20have%20to%20be%20maintained%20at%20religious%20structures%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20in%202023%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20had%20allowed%20a%20survey%20at%20Varanasi's%20Gyanvapi%20Mosque%2C%20with%20then%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20DY%20Chandrachud%20arguing%20that%20the%20Places%20of%20Worship%20(Special%20Provisions)%20Act%2C%201991%20does%20not%20debar%20ascertainment%20of%20the%20religious%20character%20of%20a%20place%20of%20worship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20pointed%20out%20by%20former%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20People's%20Democratic%20Party%20chief%20Mehbooba%20Mufti.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EClaiming%20that%20the%20violence%20at%20Sambhal%2C%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20was%20the%20direct%20result%20of%20this%20judgment%2C%20Ms%20Mufti%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThanks%20to%20a%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20a%20Pandora's%20box%20has%20been%20opened%20sparking%20a%20contentious%20debate%20about%20minority%20religious%20places%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20ruling%20that%20the%20status%20quo%20should%20be%20maintained%20as%20it%20existed%20in%201947%2C%20his%20judgement%20has%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20surveys%20of%20these%20sites%20potentially%20leading%20to%20increased%20tension%20between%20Hindus%20and%20Muslims%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20PDP%20chief%20added%2C%20citing%20the%20top%20court's%20remarks%20when%20a%20bench%20had%20decided%20that%20a%20Ram%20temple%20can%20be%20built%20in%20Ayodhya.%20Justice%20Chandrachud%20was%20part%20of%20the%20bench%20that%20gave%20this%20order%20and%20made%20the%20remark%20upholding%20the%201991%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20things%20are%20very%20painful.%20Some%20people%20have%20their%20cool%20after%202024%20(Lok%20Sabha)%20election%20results%20as%20they%20didn't%20get%20the%20majority.%20These%20people%20want%20to%20target%20a%20particular%20community%20to%20please%20the%20majority%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Samajwadi%20Party%20MP%20Mohibbullah%20Nadvi.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BWorrisome.%20The%20latest%20claim%3A%20Shiv%20Temple%20at%20Ajmer%20Dargah.%20Where%20are%20we%20taking%20this%20country%3F%20And%20why%3F%20For%20political%20dividends!%26quot%3B%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20Kapil%20Sibal%20said%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYet%20another%20shocker...%20supposedly%20hidden%20somewhere%20in%20the%20Ajmer%20Dargah%20Sharif%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20People's%20Conference%20president%20Sajad%20Gani%20Lone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAIMIM%20chief%20Asaduddin%20Owaisi%20said%20the%20if%20the%201991%20Places%20of%20Worship%20Act%20is%20followed%2C%20the%20country%20will%20be%20run%20according%20to%20the%20constitution.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnBhim%20Army%20chief%20Chadrashekhar%20Azad%20questioned%20how%20petitions%20like%20this%20are%20being%20filed%20every%20day%2C%20contending%20that%20they%20are%20%26quot%3Bdetracting%20attention%20from%20real%20issues%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhwaja%20Moinuddin%20Chishti%2C%20a%20Sufi%20saint%20from%20Persia%2C%20had%20made%20Ajmer%20his%20home%20and%20a%20shrine%20in%20his%20honour%20was%20built%20by%20Mughal%20emperor%20Humayun.%20His%20grandson%2C%20emperor%20Akbar%2C%20made%20a%20pilgrimage%20to%20Ajmer%20every%20year.%20Akbar%20and%20his%20grandson%20Shah%20Jahan%20had%20built%20mosques%20inside%20the%20Ajmer%20shrine%20complex.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20petition%20on%20Ajmer%20dargah%20has%20sought%20that%20Hindus%20be%20given%20the