inally%2C%20it%20was%20supposed%20to%20have%20one%20door%2C%20and%20they%20wanted%20two%20doors%20and%20they%20wanted%20it%20to%20open%20like%20the%20Toyota%20Sienna%20minivan%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWest%20Coast%20Customs%20can't%20reveal%20too%20much%20more%20about%20the%20specs%20and%20modifications%20of%20the%20car%20due%20to%20a%20nondisclosure%20agreement.%20But%20Friedlinghaus%20also%20said%20working%20with%20a%20car%20from%20a%20luxury%20company%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frolls-royce-porsche-sales-show-rich-arent-cutting-back-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPorsche%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20always%20a%20challenge%20since%20loyal%20followers%20of%20the%20brand%20typically%20like%20to%20adhere%20to%20original%20designs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverybody's%20such%20a%20purist%20in%20that%20space%20so%20modifying%20anything%20is%20always%20a%20challenge%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BSo%20I'm%20like%3A%20I%20need%20this%20to%20look%20good%20obviously%20for%20the%20family%20and%20for%20it%20to%20be%20functional.%20But%20what%20I%20also%20want%20is%20for%20people%20to%20look%20at%20it%20and%20be%20like%2C%20'Wow%2C%20did%20Porsche%20make%20that%3F'%20And%20I%20think%20we%20nailed%20it%20on%20that%20one.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZuckerberg's%20minivan%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20a%20one-of-a-kind%20on%20the%20roads.%20A%20Porsche%20spokesperson%20previously%20told%20BI%20in%20an%20email%20that%20the%20company%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bspecial%20wishes%26quot%3B%20department%20that%20allows%20customers%20to%20build%20their%20own%20Porsche%20to%20their%20%26quot%3Bprecise%20requirements.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20date%20we've%20not%20yet%20been%20asked%20to%20create%20a%20minivan!%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFriedlinghaus%20started%20West%20Coast%20Customs%20in%20the%20early%201990s%20with%20a%20small%20shop%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California.%20The%20sho