%20Of%20Grandmother%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra's%20entry%20into%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20was%20not%20just%20a%20political%20moment%20but%20a%20scene%20steeped%20in%20symbolism.%20Dressed%20in%20a%20Kerala%20Kasavu%20saree%2C%20Priyanka's%20attire%20instantly%20reminded%20many%20of%20a%20young%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20often%20seen%20in%20similar%20traditional%20sarees%20during%20her%20time%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPriyanka%20Gandhi's%20choice%20of%20the%20traditional%20attire%20carried%20a%20much%20deeper%20meaning%20as%20she%20stood%20to%20take%20her%20oath%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Parliament%20from%20Wayanad%20on%20Thursday%2C%20holding%20a%20copy%20of%20the%20Constitution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHer%20resemblance%20to%20Indira%20Gandhi%20was%20uncanny%2C%20with%20many%20noticing%20how%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20appearance%20brought%20back%20memories%20of%20her%20grandmother%20and%20the%20three-time%20Prime%20Minister.%20Indira%20Gandhi%2C%20who%20was%20best%20known%20for%20her%20powerful%20persona%2C%20and%20had%20often%20used%20her%20outfits%20to%20connect%20with%20the%20common%20people%2C%20and%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20choice%20of%20saree%20seemed%20to%20echo%20the%20same%20sentiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20by%20a%20media%20person%20if%20she%20remembered%20her%20grandmother%20during%20the%20oath-taking%20ceremony%2C%20Priyanka%20replied%2C%20saying%2C%20%26quot%3BYes%2C%20I%20did%20remembered%20her%2C%20and%20I%20also%20rememebered%20my%20father.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Kasavu%20saree%20is%20more%20than%20just%20an%20outfit%3B%20it%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20Kerala's%20cultural%20unity.%20Priyanka%20Gandhi's%20decision%20to%20wear%20it%20during%20the%20oath-taking%20ceremony%20also%20appeared%20as%20a%20respectful%20nod%20to%20the%20people%20of%20Wayanad%2C%20who%20elected%20her%20as%20their%20representative%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20for%20the%20oath%20ceremony%20of%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%2C