n%20Uphill%20Climb%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20times%20when%20people%20in%20urban%20India%20take%205G%20connectivity%20for%20granted%20and%20ten-minute%20doorstep%20delivery%20has%20become%20the%20norm%2C%20people%20in%20these%20tribal%20villages%20in%20Rajasthan%20have%20to%20climb%20a%20hill%2C%20literally%2C%20in%20hope%20of%20getting%20some%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Dungarpur's%20Balvania%20and%20Chaarwada%20villages%2C%20some%2035%20kilometers%20from%20the%20district%20headquarters%2C%20there%20is%20no%20telecommunication%20network%20within%20a%20radius%20of%20seven%20kilometers.%20Whether%20it%20is%20to%20call%20an%20ambulance%20or%20catch%20up%20with%20friends%20and%20family%2C%20people%20climb%20a%20small%20hill%20in%20hopes%20of%20getting%20some%20network.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20not%20just%20keeping%20in%20touch%20with%20people%20that%20is%20a%20problem%20in%20these%20villages%2C%20with%20a%20population%20of%20around%205%2C000.%20People%20here%20are%20deprived%20of%20essential%20government%20schemes%20and%20sometimes%20even%20rations%20due%20to%20network%20inaccessibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ration%20dealer%2C%20whose%20delivery%20can%20only%20be%20completed%20with%20a%20'one%20time%20password%20(OTP)'%20says%20he%20too%20has%20to%20climb%20the%20hill%20when%20delivering%20rations%20here.%20On%20the%20day%20of%20delivery%2C%20people%20say%20they%20queue%20up%20atop%20the%20hill%20rather%20than%20the%20shop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20dealer%20is%20fed%20up%20with%20delivering%20rations%20here%2C%20we%20don't%20have%20a%20tower%20and%20no%20network%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20a%20villager%20expressing%20his%20disappointment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20register%20for%20social%20welfare%20schemes%2C%20villagers%20in%20this%20tribal%20belt%20either%20try%20their%20luck%20on%20higher%20ground%20or%20trek%20to%20the%20district%20headquarters%20of%20Dungarpur%20to%20go%20online.%20Sometimes%2C%20they%20walk%20to%20Karawada%20village%2C%20some%2015%20km%20away%2C%20to%20access%20the%20state%20government's%20'e-Mitra'%20booths.%20E-Mitra%20is%20the%20Rajasthan%20government's%20initiative%20to%20deliver%20government%20and%20private%20citizen-centric%20services%20to%20people%20transparently%20and%20cost-effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20happen%20to%20drive%20along%20the%20road%20here%2C%20people%20climbing%20on%20a%20hill%20and%20waving%20their%20phones%20in%20the%20air%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20some%20network%20is%20a%20common%20sight.%20Those%20among%20them%20who%20are%20lucky%20enough%20to%20get%20some%20are%20seen%20sitting%20and%20chatting%20on%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20in%20these%20villages%2C%20nestled%20on%20the%20Rajasthan-Gujarat%20border%2C%20say%20their%20homes%20and%20settlements%20around%20the%20hills%20have%20absolutely%20no%20signal.%20%26quot%3BMy%20house%20is%201%20km%20away%20but%20I%20have%20to%20come%20here%20to%20find%20this%20hill%20and%20make%20a%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Popatlal%2C%20a%20resident%20of%20Balwania%20village.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20network%20here%20within%20the%20radius%20of%20six%20kilometers.%20The%20government%20organises%20camps%20for%20delivering%20and%20introducing%20social%20welfare%20schemes%20but%20they%20may%20as%20well%20not%20do%20that%20since%20there%20is%20no%20network%20here.%20How%20do%20we%20go%20online%20to%20access%20those%20schemes%3F%26quot%3B%20says%20Mahendra%20Ghoghra%2C%20Balwania's%20village%20head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20someone%20meets%20with%20an%20accident%2C%20we%20don't%20know%20whether%20to%20attend%20to%20the%20patient%20or%20climb%20this%20hill%20for%202%20km%20to%20call%20an%20ambulance%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20another%20villager.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20the%20children%20in%20these%20villages%20find%20it%20difficult%20to%20get%20their%20schoolwork%20done%20due%20to%20no%20connectivity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20people%20here%20have%20tried%20to%20raise%