blank%5C%22%3Eeconomic%20transformation%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20captured%20global%20attention%20but%20relies%20on%20hundreds%20of%20billions%20of%20dollars%20in%20investment%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20tourism%2C%20entertainment%2C%20and%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Saudi%20economy%20has%20contracted%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20the%20changes%20take%20place%20and%20global%20oil%20prices%20have%20declined.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Infinity%20pool%20Neom%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F663e2740f27898f532d60be8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221152%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20rendering%20of%20an%20infinity%20pool%20that%20forms%20part%20of%20Neom%20planning.%3Cp%3ENeom%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20Saudi%20Arabia%20was%20the%20fastest-growing%20G20%20economy%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.imf.org%2Fen%2FNews%2FArticles%2F2023%2F06%2F06%2Fsaudi-arabia-staff-concluding-statement-of-the-2023-article-iv-mission%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EIMF%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Its%20GDP%20contracted%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mof.gov.sa%2Fen%2FMediaCenter%2Fnews%2FPages%2FNews_3092024.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESaudi%20government%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20forecast%200.8%25%20growth%20this%20year%2C%20and%20a%20sharp%20acceleration%20in%202025%20as%20non-oil%20activities%20take%20off.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneom-saudi-arabia-economy-budget-deficit-progress-2024-11%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732793461000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67482de5fa0140cdd566125c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneom-saudi-arabia-economy-budget-deficit-progress-2024-11%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Neom%20is%20a%20long-term%20project%2C%20rather%20than%20one%20expected%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bmaking%20money%20in%20five%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Saudi%20Arabia's%20finance%20minister.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22pthompson%40insider.com%20(Polly%20Thompson)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fneom-saudi-arabia-economy-budget-deficit-progress-2024-11%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEverest%20Of%20Corporate%20Turnarounds%26quot%3B%3A%20Air%20India%20CEO%20On%20Company's%20Revival%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUnder%20fire%20for%20faltering%20service%20standards%2C%20staff%20disputes%20and%20aircraft%20with%20severely%20dated%20interiors%2C%20Campbell%20Wilson%2C%20the%20MD%20and%20CEO%20of%20Air%20India%20has%20told%20NDTV%20that%20the%20revival%20of%20the%20airline%20will%20take%20a%20few%20more%20years%20to%20complete.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BThe%20Economist%20called%20this%20the%20Everest%20of%20corporate%20turn-arounds%2C''%20said%20Mr.%20Wilson.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20made%20no%20secret%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20it%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20multi-year%20programme.''%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20year%202%20of%20a%205-year%20transformation%20programme%2C%20the%20management%20of%20Air%20India%20has%20faced%20an%20uphill%20battle%20to%20integrate%20thousands%20of%20workers%20across%20airlines%20that%20are%20now%20part%20of%20the%20group%20-%20Vistara%2C%20Air%20India%20Express%20and%20Air%20Asia%20India.%20%C2%A0Each%20airline%2C%20including%20the%20original%20Air%20India%20has%20had%20its%20own%20work%20culture%20-%20bringing%20the%20job%20expectations%20of%20personnel%20into%20line%20has%20been%20particularly%20challenging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVistara%20pilots%20effectively%20went%20on%20a%20form%20of%20strike%20by%20calling%20in%20sick%20en%20masse%2C%20starting%20notably%20towards%20the%20end%20of%20March%202024%2C%20with%20significant%20disruptions%20continuing%20into%20early%20April%202024.%20This%20was%20a%20protest%20against%20new%20contracts%20introduced%20due%20to%20Vistara's%20impending%20merger%20with%20Air%20India%2C%20which%20reduced%20their%20guaranteed%20flying%20hours%20from%2070%20to%2040%20hours%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20pay%20cut%20for%20many%20pilots%2C%20particularly%20junior%20first%20officers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20May%20this%20year%2C%20Air%20India%20Express%20cabin%20crew%20went%20on%20strike%20when%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20cabin%20crew%20members%20began%20reporting%20sick%20to%20protest%20against%20alleged%20mismanagement%20and%20issues%20related%20to%20their%20merger%20with%20AIX%20Connect%20(formerly%20AirAsia%20India).%20After%20initially%20dismissing%20several%20cabin%20crew%20members%2C%20the%20airline%20management%20reinstated%20them%20after%20mediation%20by%20India's%20Chief%20Labour%20Commissioner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20certainly%20not%20the%20finished%20product.%20%C2%A0I%20know%20that%20there's%20a%20huge%20amount%20of%20expectation%20and%20indeed%20impatience%20for%20the%20future%20Air%20India%20to%20fully%20emerge%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Cambell%20Wilson.%20%C2%A0''I%20am%20equally%20impatient%20for%20that%20to%20happen%2C''%20he%20says%2C%20pointing%20out%20that%20despite%20the%20hiccups%2C%20there%20have%20still%20been%20massive%20changes%20in%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20airline.%20%C2%A0''We've%20brought%20the%20average%20age%20%5Bof%20staff%20members%5D%20from%2054%20to%20to%2035%2C%209%2C000%20new%20staff%2C%20brought%204%20airlines%20into%202%2C%20140%20IT%20systems%2C%20a%20100%20new%20aircraft%2C%20new%20training%20academies%20%5Band%5D%20started%20a%20base%20maintenance%20facility.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20being%20fined%20for%20deficient%20safety%20practices%2C%20Mr.%20Wilson%20acknowledged%20occasional%20systemic%20gaps%2C%20some%20of%20which%20could%20be%20explained%20through%20legacy%20practices%20within%20the%20former%20government%20carrier.%20%C2%A0''Sometimes%20it's%20legacy%20practice.%20Sometimes%20it%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20human%20oversight.%20Sometimes%20it's%20a%20matter%20of%20a%20systemic%20gap%20or%20something%20that%20hasn't%20been%20addressed%20or%20mitigated%20through%20another%20means%2C''%20said%20Mr.%20Campbell.%20%C2%A0''%20We%20open%20ourselves%20for%20audit%20every%206%20months.%20We%20open%20ourselves%20for%20external%20audit%2C%20whether%20by%20IATA%20%5BInternational%20Air%20Travel%20Association%5D%20or%20other%20parties.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBetween%20January%20and%20August%20this%20year%2C%20Air%20India%20has%20been%20fined%20at%20least%20Rs.2.8%20crore%20by%20India's%20aviation%20regulator%2C%20the%20Director%20General%20of%20Civil%20Aviation%20(DCGA)%20for%20a%20host%20of%20safety-related%20concerns%20linked%20to%20operations%20over%20long-range%20critical%20routes%2C%20violating%20the%20flight%20duty%20time%20limitations%20of%20its%20operating%20crews%20and%20for%20operating%20an%20international%20flight%20with%20'non-qualified'%20crew%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India's%20decision%20to%20proceed%20with%20its%20planned%20merger%20with%20Vistara%2C%20widely%20considered%20India's%20finest%20full-service%20airline%2C%20has%20also%20raised%20concerns%20among%20passengers%20and%20fans%20of%20Vistara%20who%20have%20consistently%20appreciated%20the%20former%20airline's%20renowned%20service%20standards.%20%C2%A0%20Earlier%20this%20year%2C%20Vistara%20was%20adjudged%20the%20best%20airline%20in%20India%20%26amp%3B%20South%20Asia%20for%20the%20fourth%20consecutive%20year%20at%20the%202024%20World%20Airline%20Awards%20by%20Skytrax.%20%C2%A0Vistara%20aircraft%2C%20now%20integrated%20with%20Air%20India%2C%20are%20also%20configured%20to%20a%20higher-standard%20than%20a%20large%20majority%20of%20Air%20India%20existing%20A-320s%20and%20A-321.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Vistara%20now%20allows%20Air%20India%20the%20opportunity%20to%20be%20catalyzed%20and%20the%20transformation%20accelerated%20at%20a%20new%20airline%20which%20represents%20the%20best%20of%20both%20Vistara%20and%20the%20legacy%20of%20Air%20India%20to%20be%20born%2C''%20says%20Mr.%20Wilson.%20%C2%A0In%20order%20to%20be%20consistent%20with%20the%20quality%20offered%20by%20the%20Vistara%20product%2C%20Air%20India%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20continue%20flying%20erstwhile%20Vistara%20Airbus%20A320neo%20aircraft%20on%20key%20metro%20routes%20between%20Delhi-Mumbai%2C%20Delhi-Bengaluru%2C%20Delhi-Hyderabad%2C%20Delhi-Hyderabad%2C%20Mumbai-Bengaluru%20and%20Mumbai-Hyderabad%20from%20December%201.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20month%20has%20seen%20hundreds%20of%20hoax%20calls%20being%20made%20to%20airlines%20in%20India%20resulting%20in%20flight%20diversions%20and%20chaos%20on%20the%20ground%20and%20in%20the%20air%2C%20not%20just%20over%20Indian%20airspace%20but%20around%20the%20world.%20%C2%A0Several%20Air%20India%20flights%20were%20also%20impacted%2C%20tense%20times%20for%20the%20management%20of%20the%20airline%20having%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20unpredictable%20situation.%20%C2%A0%20An%20Air%20India%20Boeing%20777%20was%20forced%20to%20land%20in%20the%20sub-Arctic%20Canadian%20town%20of%20Iqaluit%20on%20October%2015%2C%202024%2C%20after%20receiving%20a%20bomb%20threat.%20%C2%A0Passengers%20were%20eventually%20flown%20to%20their%20final%20destination%2C%20Chicago%2C%20by%20the%20Royal%20Canadian%20Air%20Force%20since%20there%20were%20minimal%20support%20facilities%20to%20sustain%20so%20many%20passengers%20in%20Iqaluit.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJust%20the%20sheer%20number%20and%20and%20the%20duration%20over%20which%20these%20threats%20persisted%2C%20was%2C%20I%20think%2C%20globally%20unprecedented%2C%20said%20Mr.Campbell.%20%C2%A0''But%20it%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20aviation%20that%20there%20is%20going%20to%20be%20some%20event%20that%20wakes%20you%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20global%20conflict%20somewhere%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20a%20a%20hoax%2C%20whether%20it%20is%20you%20know%2C%20a%20snowstorm%20in%20New%20York%20that's%20caused%20some%20aircraft%20to%20divert%20to%20Pittsburgh%20or%20elsewhere.%20%C2%A0That%20that%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20the%20game%2C%20and%20so%20it's%20part%20and%20parcel%20of%20the%20job.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAirlines%20in%20India%20still%20do%20not%20know%20who%20caused%20the%20hoax%20calls.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BWe%20don't%20know%20what%20the%20cause%20was%2C%20to%20be%20honest%2C%20because%20we%20we're%20a%20private%20organization.%20We%20don't%20have%20the%20ability%20to%20go%20back%20and%20identify%20exactly%20who%20and%20why%20they%20did%20what%20they%20did.%20But%20I%20think%20what%20it%20resulted%20in%20is%20at%20the%20regulatory%20and%20industry%20level%2C%20there%20were%20new%20protocols%20and%20procedures%20put%20in%20place%20to%20more%20consistently%20and%20in%20a%20more%20timely%20fashion%20with%20more%20expertise%2C%20make%20a%20quick%20assessment%20of%20what%20was%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20threat%2C%20what%20was%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20threat%2C%20and%20therefore%20what%20actions%20should%20be%20recommended%20or%20taken.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAir%20India's%20biggest%20concern%2C%20arguably%2C%20is%20the%20long%20overdue%20fleet%20restoration%20of%20its%20existing%20long-haul%20jetliners%20including%20legacy%20Boeing%20777s%20and%20787%20Dreamliners%20which%20it%20acquired%20from%20the%20government%20when%20the%20airline%20came%20into%20its%20fold.%20%C2%A0%20These%20are%20meant%20to%20complement%20its%20record%20470%20aircraft%20order%20from%20Airbus%20and%20Boeing%2C%20a%20%2470%20billion%20deal%20that%20it%20closed%20out%20on%20February%202023.%20This%20remains%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20single%20deals%20in%20the%20history%20of%20commercial%20aviation.%20The%20refurbishment%20of%20the%20existing%20fleet%20will%20cost%20the%20group%20%24400%20million.%20This%20includes%20the%20overhaul%20of%20cabin%20interiors%20for%20its%20wide-body%20fleet%2C%20comprising%2027%20Boeing%20B787-8%20and%2013%20Boeing%20B777%20aircraft.%20Single-aisle%20aircraft%20-%20the%20Airbus%20A320neo%20and%20A321neo%20are%20also%20being%20upgraded%2C%20a%20process%20that%20has%20already%20begun.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''It's%20fair%20to%20say%20that%2C%20particularly%2C%20the%20legacy%20aircraft%20that%20we%20inherited%2C%20were%20not%20up%20to%20that%20standard%2C%20and%20it%20just%20takes%20a%20long%20time.%20We%20have%20committed%20%24400%20million%20to%20buy%20the%20seats%20to%20refurbish%20those%20aircraft.%20The%20seats%20have%20been%20in%20the%20certification%20and%20manufacturing%20process%20since%20then.%20They%20will%20be%20start%20to%20be%20installed%20on%20the%20wide%20body%20aircraft%20next%20year.%20The%20problem%20Air%20India%20faces%20with%20the%20pace%20of%20refurbishment%20of%20its%20older%20aircraft%20is%20an%20industry-wide%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Two%20different%20seat%20suppliers%2C%20reflecting%20just%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20post-COVID%20supply%20chain%2C%20came%20to%20us%20and%20said%2C%20the%20dates%20we%20committed%20to%20deliver%2C%20we%20can%20no%20longer%20meet.%20There's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20delay%20of%2C%20in%20one%20case%2C%206%20months%2C%20in%20one%20case%2C%20a%20little%20bit%20longer.''%20%C2%A0This%20has%20meant%20that%20legacy%20Air%20India%20Boeing%20787s%20and%20777s%20which%20are%20scheduled%20for%20refurbishment%20%C2%A0will%20see%20a%20new%20and%20vastly%20improved%20interior%20product%20only%20from%20mid-2025%20onwards.%20%C2%A0%26quot%3BUnfortunately%2C%20it%20is%20what%20it%20is.%20We%20don't%20have%20any%20control%20of%20that.%20Many%20other%20airlines%20are%20affected%20by%20similar%20constraints.''%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20set%20of%20new-generation%20Boeing%20787%20Dreamliner%20seats%20arrive%20in%20April%2C%20will%20be%20installed%20and%20then%20certified%20for%20use%2C%20''though%20not%20before%20October%20next%20year.%20%C2%A0The%20pace%20of%20the%20upgrade%20will%20then%20pick%20up%20with%20a%20couple%20of%20Boeing%20787%20Dreamliner%20aircraft%20entering%20the%20refurbishment%20process%20every%20month.%20%C2%A0Air%20India's%20large-capacity%20Boeing%20777%2C%20which%20have%20operated%20long-haul%20routes%20primarily%20to%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20will%20take%20longer%20to%20upgrade.%20%C2%A0While%20there%20will%20be%20an%20interim%20refresh%20to%20the%20product%20on%20existing%20aircraft%20during%202025%2C%20the%20full%20cabin%20refresh%20will%20only%20happen%20in%202026.%20%C2%A0''As%20I%20say%20at%20the%20end%20of%202026%2C%20the%20refurbishment%20to%20be%20well%20underway.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20meanwhile%2C%20Air%20India%20has%20introduced%206-brand%20new%20Airbus%20A-350-900%20aircraft%20onto%20its%20flagship%20routes%20-%20New%20York%20and%20London%20with%20services%20commencing%20to%20Newark%20within%20weeks.%20%C2%A0While%20this%20is%20a%20welcome%20addition%20to%20the%20hard-product%20offered%20by%20the%20legacy%20carrier%2C%20the%20truly%20new%20Air%20India%20is%20still%20years%20away%20from%20being%20realised.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECampbell%20Wilson%20realises%20this.%20%C2%A0''We%20carry%2060%20million%20people%20a%20year%20across%20the%20group.%20We%20operate%20more%20than%201200%20flights%20every%20day.%20And%20so%2C%20it%20is%20a%20mass%20transportation%20business%2C%20and%20unfortunately%2C%20you%20know%2C%20there%20are%20occasions%20where%20it's%20not%20perfect%2C''%20says%20Mr.Wilson.%20%C2%A0%20''It's%20just%20that%20we%20have%20to%20be%20more%20consistent%20and%20continue%20that%20process%20because%20I'm%20as%20impatient%20as%20anyone%20of%20improving%20this%20to%20the%20level%20that%2C%20you%20know%2C%20meets%20customer%20expectations%20all%20the%20time.''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732793460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-08%2F6tqpb1h_air-i