e%20INDIA%20Opposition%20bloc%20were%20in%20Ranchi's%20Moradabad%20Ground%20to%20attend%20the%20swearing-in%20ceremony.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20Samajwadi%20Party%20chief%20Akhilesh%20Yadav%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20Trinamool%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20leader%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20and%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%20attended%20the%20event.%20Hemant%20Soren%20was%20the%20only%20one%20to%20take%20oath%20today%20as%20the%20Mahagathbandhan%20allies%20are%20still%20negotiating%20over%20cabinet%20berths.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20state%20polls%2C%20results%20of%20which%20were%20declared%20on%20Saturday%2C%20the%20JMM-led%20alliance%20won%2056%20seats%20in%20the%2081-member%20House.%20The%20Hemant%20Soren-led%20party%2C%20which%20contested%2041%20seats%2C%20won%2034%2C%20and%20the%20Congress%20managed%20victory%20on%2016%20out%20of%2030%20seats.%20RJD%20and%20CPIML%20won%20six%20and%20four%20seats%2C%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-nine-year-old%20Hemant%20Soren%20started%20his%20political%20career%20with%20a%20short%20stint%20in%20Rajya%20Sabha%20before%20becoming%20an%20MLA%20in%202009.%20He%20served%20as%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20from%202010%20to%202013%20when%20JMM%20was%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20BJP%20and%20Arjun%20Munda%20was%20Chief%20Minister.%20Later%20in%202013%2C%20he%20became%20Chief%20Minister%20with%20the%20JMM%20tying%20up%20with%20the%20Congress%20and%20RJD.%20In%20the%202014%20state%20election%2C%20the%20BJP%20came%20to%20power%20and%20Mr%20Soren%20took%20over%20as%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20the%20Assembly.%20The%20JMM-Congress%20alliance%20won%20the%202019%20Assembly%20election%20and%20Mr%20Soren%20started%20his%20second%20stint%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20he%20was%20arrested%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20a%20money%20laundering%20case.%20Mr%20Soren%20has%20denied%20the%20charges%20and%20accused%20the%20BJP%20of%20using%20probe%20agencies%20for%20political%20goals.%20Ahead%20of%20his%20arrest%2C%20he%20resigned%20and%20his%20close%20aide%20Champai%20Soren%20took%20over%20as%20Chief%20Minister.%20After%20over%20six%20months%20in%20jail%2C%20Mr%20Soren%20was%20granted%20bail.%20When%20he%20moved%20to%20take%20over%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20again%2C%20Champai%20Soren%20quit%20the%20JMM%2C%20alleging%20that%20he%20was%20humiliated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Soren's%20arrest%20and%20imprisonment%20also%20brought%20his%20wife%20Kalpana%20to%20the%20political%20stage.%20Ms%20Soren%20campaigned%20extensively%20and%20attended%20grand%20meetings%20of%20the%20Opposition%20parties%20in%20her%20husband's%20absence.%20In%20this%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20she%20was%20elected%20as%20an%20MLA%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20had%20pushed%20hard%20to%20score%20a%20victory%20in%20Jharkhand%2C%20with%20its%20top%20leaders%20travelling%20to%20the%20state%20during%20the%20poll%20campaign.%20Its%20campaign%20accused%20the%20ruling%20party%20of%20aiding%20the%20infiltration%20of%20Bangladesh%20refugees%2C%20among%20other%20issues.%20But%20the%20Hemant%20Soren%20government's%20public%20welfare%20schemes%20and%20the%20sympathy%20wave%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20his%20arrest%20trumped%20the%20BJP's%20poll%20push%20and%20brought%20JMM%20back%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732793160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F3ebri0vg_hemant-soren_625x300_28_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhemant-soren-takes-oath-as-jharkhand-chief-minister-for-fourth-time-7125679%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20(JMM)%20leader%20Hemant%20Soren%20took%20oath%20as%20Chief%20Minister%20today%2C%20days%20after%20the%20INDIA%20bloc's%20decisive%20victory%20in%