2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCongress's%20Overconfidence%20Cost%20Us%26quot%3B%3A%20Team%20Thackeray%20On%20Maharashtra%20Rout%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress's%20%26quot%3Boverconfidence%26quot%3B%20in%20Maharashtra%20and%20its%20%26quot%3Battitude%26quot%3B%20during%20seat-sharing%20talks%20hurt%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi's%20prospects%2C%20a%20senior%20leader%20of%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20has%20said%20a%20week%20after%20the%20Opposition%20bloc%20was%20routed%20in%20the%20state%20polls.%20The%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20scored%20a%20thumping%20victory%20in%20the%20election%2C%20winning%20230%20seats%20in%20the%20288-member%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmbadas%20Danve%2C%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20in%20Maharashtra%20Legislative%20Council%20said%20that%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20should%20have%20projected%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20as%20its%20Chief%20Minister%20face.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20results%2C%20the%20Congress%20was%20overconfident%20in%20Maharashtra%20like%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir.%20This%20was%20reflected%20in%20the%20results.%20Its%20attitude%20during%20seat-sharing%20negotiations%20hurt%20us.%20Uddhav%20ji%20should%20have%20been%20projected%20as%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20face.%20Not%20doing%20so%20harmed%20our%20prospects.%20The%20results%20would%20have%20been%20different%20if%20this%20was%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Danve%20told%20the%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20subtle%20dig%20at%20the%20Congress%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20were%20getting%20ready%20with%20suit%20and%20tie%20even%20before%20the%20results.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20won%2013%20seats%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20months%20ago%2C%20the%20highest%20among%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20allies.%20Buoyed%20by%20the%20stellar%20show%2C%20the%20Nana%20Patole-led%20state%20Congress%20unit%20bargained%20hard%20during%20the%20seat-sharing%20talks%20ahead%20of%20the%20state%20polls%2C%20leading%20to%20friction%20in%20the%20alliance.%20Eventually%2C%20it%20contested%20103%20seats%20but%20won%20only%2016.%20The%20Sena%20(UBT)%2C%20which%20contested%2089%20seats%2C%20managed%20to%20win%2020%20seats.%20The%20third%20ally%2C%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20NCP%2C%20contested%2087%20seats%20and%20won%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Danve%20said%20some%20of%20the%20candidates%20of%20Sena%20(UBT)%20had%20pointed%20to%20the%20organisational%20aspect%2C%20but%20did%20not%20name%20any%20party.%20He%20said%20Sena%20(UBT)%20will%20prepare%20to%20build%20its%20strength%20to%20the%20point%20where%20it%20can%20contest%20all%20288%20seats%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20his%20former%20party%20colleague%20and%20former%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde%2C%20whose%20rebellion%20split%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%2C%20Mr%20Danve%20said%20the%20BJP%20has%20%26quot%3Bmany%20Shindes%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20has%20many%20Shindes%20in%20several%20states.%20The%20BJP%20uses%20and%20throws%20them%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20remarks%20come%20amid%20talks%20within%20the%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20on%20who%20will%20be%20the%20next%20Chief%20Minister.%20The%20BJP%20has%20scored%20the%20highest%20among%20NDA%20allies%20and%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20pushed%20for%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%20After%20days%20of%20posturing%20by%20some%20Sena%20leaders%2C%20Mr%20Shinde%20yesterday%20stepped%20back%20and%20said%20he%20would%20accept%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20decision%20on%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20post.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732790280000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2F0e843gm_uddhav-sharad-pawar-rahul-gandhi_625x300_25_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2024-maharashtra-election-results-congresss-overconfidence-cost-us-team-thackeray-leader-after-poll-rout-7125629%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Congress's%20%26quot%3Boverconfidence%