22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fas-if-we-werent-suffering-enough-australian-pm-pokes-virat-kohli-gets-epic-reply-7124721%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lashkar%20Terrorist%2C%20Accused%20Of%20Terror%20Activities%20In%20Bengaluru%2C%20Extradited%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESalman%20Rehman%20Khan%2C%20a%20terrorist%20belonging%20to%20the%20banned%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%2C%20was%20extradited%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%20from%20Rwanda%20today.%20Salman%20was%20implicated%20in%20the%20Bengaluru%20Prisons%20Terror%20Conspiracy%20case%2C%20where%20investigations%20revealed%20his%20involvement%20in%20radicalisation%20and%20the%20supply%20of%20explosives%20to%20terror%20operatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20collaboration%20of%20the%20Rwanda%20Investigation%20Bureau%20(RIB)%2C%20Interpol%2C%20and%20National%20Central%20Bureaus%20(NCBs)%2C%20Salman%20was%20arrested%20in%20Rwanda's%20capital%20Kigali%20yesterday.%20He%20was%20transferred%20to%20India%20early%20Thursday%2C%20where%20he%20was%20formally%20taken%20into%20custody%20by%20the%20NIA.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20marks%20the%2017th%20instance%20since%202020%20where%20the%20NIA%20has%20successfully%20facilitated%20the%20extradition%20or%20deportation%20of%20terror-related%20fugitives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESalman%20was%20lodged%20in%20Bengaluru%20Central%20Prison%2C%20where%20he%20was%20serving%20a%20sentence%20for%20a%20POCSO%20(Protection%20of%20Children%20from%20Sexual%20Offenses)%20conviction%20between%202018%20and%202022.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20incarceration%20that%20Salman%20came%20into%20contact%20with%20T%20Naseer%2C%20a%20convicted%20terrorist%20serving%20a%20life%20sentence.%20Investigations%20revealed%20that%20Naseer%20played%20a%20role%20in%20radicalising%20Salman%20and%20orchestrating%20a%20terror%20module%20within%20the%20prison%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA's%20probe%20exposed%20how%20Salman%2C%20upon%20being%20radicalised%2C%20became%20an%20active%20participant%20in%20terror%20activities.%20He%20assisted%20in%20the%20procurement%20and%20distribution%20of%20arms%2C%20ammunition%2C%20and%20explosives%20for%20terror%20operatives.%20Naseer%20also%20masterminded%20plots%20to%20facilitate%20his%20own%20escape%20during%20court%20appearances%2C%20a%20plan%20in%20which%20Salman%20was%20a%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20the%20terror%20conspiracy%20was%20uncovered%2C%20Salman%20fled%20India%2C%20evading%20authorities%20until%20his%20arrest%20in%20Rwanda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Salman%20Was%20Arrested%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NIA%20had%20registered%20the%20Bengaluru%20Prisons%20Terror%20Conspiracy%20case%20on%20October%2025%20last%20year%2C%20taking%20over%20from%20Bengaluru%20City%20Police.%20Salman%2C%20already%20declared%20a%20fugitive%2C%20was%20charged%20under%20the%20stringent%20UAPA%2C%20the%20Arms%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20Explosive%20Substances%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Red%20Notice%20was%20issued%20by%20Interpol%20at%20the%20request%20of%20the%20NIA%20on%20August%202%20this%20year.%20Authorities%20in%20Rwanda%2C%20acting%20on%20the%20notice%2C%20arrested%20Salman%20and%20notified%20Indian%20agencies.%20This%20led%20to%20a%20series%20of%20coordinated%20efforts%20between%20the%20NIA%2C%20the%20Rwandan%20National%20Central%20Bureau%20(NCB)%2C%20and%20Interpol%2C%20ultimately%20resulting%20in%20Salman's%20extradition.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%20alone%2C%2026%20fugitives%20were%20returned%20to%20India%20through%20coordinated%20efforts%20involving%20Interpol.%20These%20include%20individuals%20accused%20of%20crimes%20ranging%20from%20terror%20to%20sexual%20offences%2C%20such%20as%20Raihan%20Arabikkalalarikkal%2C%20wanted%20for%20crimes%20against%20minors%2C%20who%20was%20extradited%20from%20Saudi%20Arabia.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732783980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F20