originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsonu-sood-calls-for-safer-roads-after-young-boys-tragic-death-in-mumbai-accident%2Farticleshow%2F115763201.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F115763201.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3ESonu%20Sood%20expressed%20deep%20sorrow%20over%20a%20young%20boy's%20tragic%20death%20in%20a%20Mumbai%20road%20accident%2C%20urging%20for%20water-filled%20barriers%20on%20road%20dividers%20to%20enhance%20safety.%20He%20highlighted%20the%20Government%20of%20India's%20goal%20to%20reduce%20road%20fatalities%20by%2050%25%20by%202030.%20Sood%20will%20co-star%20with%20Jacqueline%20Fernandez%20in%20'Fateh'%2C%20releasing%20January%2010%2C%202025.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fsonu-sood-calls-for-safer-roads-after-young-boys-tragic-death-in-mumbai-accident%2Farticleshow%2F115763201.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIf%20They%20Lose%2C%20They%20Cry.%20But%20If%20They%20Win...%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20Mocks%20Congress%20On%20EVMs%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20taken%20potshots%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20complaints%20about%20faulty%20EVMs%2C%20or%20electronic%20voting%20machines%2C%20which%20it%20blames%20for%20defeats%20in%20the%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP's%20X%20handle%20took%20a%20sharp%20jab%20at%20its%20rival%2C%20pointing%20out%20the%20technology%20-%20which%20the%20Congress%20has%20repeatedly%20claimed%20can%20be%2C%20and%20is%2C%20hacked%20to%20ensure%20the%20BJP%20wins%20-%20also%20delivered%20a%20win%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20a%20record%20victory%20for%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20in%20the%20Wayanad%20Lok%20Sabha%20bypoll.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20they%20lose%2C%20they%20start%20crying%20about%20EVMs.%20And%2C%20if%20they%20win%2C%20the%20Congress%20wins...%20It%20is%20not%20the%20EVM%2C%20it%20is%20the%20Congress'%20intentions%20that%20are%20bad!%26quot%3B%20the%20BJP%20said%20in%20a%20Hindi%20post%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20post%20was%20an%20image%20of%20Rahul%20Gandhi%20celebrating%20his%20sister's%20Wayanad%20win.%20That%20image%20was%20sandwiched%20between%20pictures%20of%20an%20EVM%20and%20the%20messages%20-%20%26quot%3BHaryana%2C%20Maharashtra%20was%20lost%20because%20of%20EVMs%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BWayanad%20was%20won%20because%20of%20Rahul%20and%20Priyanka's%20strength%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20post%20came%20a%20day%20after%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi%20alliance%20of%20the%20Congress%2C%20and%20the%20Shiv%20Sena%20and%20NCP%20factions%20led%20by%20Uddhav%20Thackeray%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar%20held%20an%20anti-EVM%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20row%20over%20EVMs%20rears%20its%20head%20after%20every%20major%20election%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20accusing%20the%20BJP%20of%20engineering%20victories%20by%20hacking%20the%20machines.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20has%20steadily%20refuted%20the%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20snapbacks%20this%20week%2C%20after%20a%20thumping%20win%20for%20the%20BJP-led%20Mahayuti%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra%20-%20have%20been%20led%20by%20senior%20party%20leader%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%2C%20who%20is%20widely%20expected%20to%20be%20named%20Chief%20Minister%20for%20a%20third%20time.%20Speaking%20to%20reporters%20after%20the%20BJP's%20win%20was%20all%20but%20confirmed%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BJMM%20(and%20Congress)%20won%20in%20Jharkhand....The%20election%20there%20was%20'fair'...%20but%20if%20we%20get%20a%20huge%20victory%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20then%20Election%20Commission%20is%20'biased'%20and%20EVMs%20were%20'hacked'%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20repeated%20claims%20about%20the%20credibility%20of%20EVMs%20after%20last%20month's%20Haryana%20election%20result.%20The%20party%20was%20expected%2C%20exit%20polls%20said%20so%2C%20to%20claim%20a%20convincing%20win%20in%20the%20heartland%20state%2C%20only%20for%20the%20BJP%20to%20script%20a%20late%20comeback%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20a%20comfortable%20victory.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20furious%20Congress%20refused%20to%20accept%20the%20verdict%2C%20insisting%20EVMs%20had%20been%20hacked%20and%20raising%20questions%20about%20alleged%20delays%20in%20the%20Election%20Commission%20publishing%20voting%20data%20on%20its%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20EC%20hit%20back%20hard%2C%20criticising%20the%20Congress%20for%20making%20%26quot%3Bbaseless%20allegations...%20when%20faced%20with%20inconvenient%20electoral%20outcomes%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20warned%20it%2C%20and%20other%20parties%2C%20against%20%26quot%3Bunfounded%20and%20sensational%20complaints%26quot%3B%20during%20an%20election%2C%20including%20when%20votes%20are%20cast%20and%20then%20counted.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732783800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2F8kee3dd8_evm_625x300_17_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevm-row-bjp-congress-if-they-lose-they-cry-but-if-they-win-bjp-mocks-congress-on-evms-7124843%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20BJP%20has%20taken%20potshots%20at%20the%20Congress%20over%20complaints%20about%20faulty%20EVMs%2C%20or%20electronic%20voting%20machines%2C%20which%20it%20blames%20for%20defeats%20in%20the%20Haryana%20and%20Maharashtra%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fevm-row-bjp-congress-if-they-lose-they-cry-but-if-they-win-bjp-mocks-congress-on-evms-7124843%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Delhi's%20Prashant%20Vihar%20area%20hit%20by%20exp