ign%20promise%20of%20a%2010%20percent%20levy%20on%20all%20US%20imports%20--%20will%20spark%20retaliation%20and%20have%20ripple%20effects%20across%20the%20global%20economy%2C%20analysts%20say.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20assumption%20is%20that%20all%20these%20other%20countries%2C%20all%20these%20other%20advanced%20economies%2C%20especially%20in%20Asia%2C%20they%20will%20retaliate%20in%20kind%2C%26quot%3B%20economist%20Bernard%20Yaros%20of%20Oxford%20Economics%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUS%20tariffs%20and%20retaliation%20including%20from%20Europe%20and%20Asia%20would%20%26quot%3Bdepress%20growth%26quot%3B%20and%20trade%20flows%2C%20he%20said%2C%20estimating%20a%20cut%20to%20global%20growth%20of%200.1%20to%200.9%20percentage%20points%20in%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20before%20tariffs%20take%20effect%2C%20threats%20weigh%20on%20sentiment%20and%20could%20delay%20investments%20and%20hiring%2C%20ING%20economists%20Ruben%20Dewitte%20and%20Inga%20Fechner%20warned%20in%20a%20note.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump%20has%20long%20viewed%20tariffs%20as%20a%20negotiating%20tool%20--%20or%20an%20%26quot%3Ball-purpose%20bludgeon%26quot%3B%20as%20a%20recent%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20editorial%20put%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Monday%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20the%20tariffs%20on%20Mexico%20and%20Canada%20would%20only%20be%20removed%20when%20illegal%20immigration%20and%20drug%20trafficking%20to%20the%20United%20States%20are%20stopped.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20seeking%20to%20build%20US%20leverage%2C%20he%20also%20risks%20longer%20term%20impacts%2C%20with%20some%20suggesting%20he%20would%20push%20countries%20toward%20China%2C%20Columbia%20Law%20School%20professor%20Petros%20Mavroidis%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20he%20definitely%20does%20is%20alienate%20all%20his%20allies%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20AFP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EErin%20Murphy%2C%20senior%20fellow%20at%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20International%20Studies%2C%20said%20in%20Trump's%20threats%20%26quot%3Bthere%20is%20no%20differentiation%26quot%3B%20regarding%20countries'%20economic%20development%20status%20or%20affinity%20with%20Washington.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EEurope%20pushback%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEurope%20could%20be%20particularly%20impacted%2C%20Dewitte%20and%20Fechner%20said%2C%20warning%20that%20%26quot%3Ba%20looming%20new%20trade%20war%20could%20push%20the%20eurozone%20economy%20from%20sluggish%20growth%20into%20recession.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20tariffs%20on%20car%20imports%20were%20a%20particular%20target%20of%20Trump%20during%20his%20campaign.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20US%20reliance%20on%20the%20bloc%20for%20strategically%20important%20products%2C%20mainly%20in%20the%20chemical%20and%20pharmaceutical%20sectors%2C%20could%20give%20the%20EU%20some%20leverage%20in%20talks%2C%20ING%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEuropean%20countries%20will%20be%20less%20likely%20to%20strike%20any%20kind%20of%20bargain%20with%20Trump%20than%20Canada%20or%20Mexico%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Peterson%20Institute%20for%20International%20Economics%20nonresident%20senior%20fellow%20Gary%20Hufbauer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20expects%20the%20EU%20could%20offer%20to%20reduce%20auto%20tariffs%20and%20buy%20more%20US%20agricultural%20products%20like%20soybeans%2C%20but%20it%20may%20not%20be%20enough%20for%20an%20administration%20seeking%20greater%20market%20access%20or%20rules%20exemptions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShould%20the%20US%20impose%20tariffs%2C%20the%20EU%20will%20probably%20retaliate%20on%20iconic%20US%20goods%20like%20iPhones%20or%20whiskey%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEuropean%20countries%20could%20turn%20to%20the%20World%20Trade%20Organization%20(WTO)%2C%20though%20even%20favorable%20rulings%20from%20the%20international%20body%20may%20not%20significantly%20change%20US%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEU%20chief%20Ursula%20von%20der%20Leyen%20has%20said%20she%20will%20work%20towards%20%26quot%3Bconstructive%20coo