Consciousness%20(ISKCON)%20community%20as%20Sri%20Chinmay%20Krishna%20Prabhu%2C%20is%20an%20influential%20religious%20leader%20in%20Bangladesh.%20As%20President%20of%20Pundarik%20Dham%2C%20an%20ISKCON%20centre%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20he%20has%20long%20been%20a%20voice%20for%20those%20seeking%20religious%20freedom%20and%20minority%20protection.%20He%20previously%20held%20the%20position%20of%20divisional%20organising%20secretary%20for%20ISKCON%20in%20Chattogram.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHe%20was%20born%20in%20May%201985%20in%20Karianagar%20village%2C%20located%20in%20the%20Satkania%20Upazila%20of%20Chattogram.%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20Brahmachari%20gained%20recognition%20for%20his%20skills%20as%20a%20child%20orator%20within%20religious%20circles.%20His%20spiritual%20journey%20began%20at%20a%20young%20age%2C%20and%20by%201997%2C%20at%20just%2012%20years%20old%2C%20he%20took%20diksha%20(initiation)%20and%20joined%20ISKCON%20as%20a%20brahmachari.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EBrahmachari's%20arrest%20came%20after%20a%20high-profile%20rally%20in%20Chittagong%20on%20October%2025%2C%202024.%20The%20precise%20motive%20behind%20the%20charges%20against%20Brahmachari%20remains%20unclear%2C%20but%20reports%20indicate%20that%20he%20faces%20accusations%20of%20disrespecting%20the%20Bangladeshi%20flag%20during%20a%20protest%20rally.%20Das%2C%20along%20with%2018%20others%2C%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20sedition.%20Just%20days%20before%20his%20arrest%2C%20on%20November%2022%2C%20he%20spoke%20at%20a%20rally%20in%20Rangpur%2C%20denouncing%20the%20acts%20of%20violence%20on%20the%20Hindu%20community.%20On%20November%2026%2C%20a%20Bangladesh%20court%20denied%20Das's%20bail%20petition%20and%20ordered%20his%20detention.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20few%20months%20ago%2C%20Brahmachari%20was%20relatively%20unknown.%20His%20rise%20to%20prominence%20began%20when%20violence%20erupted%20against%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20Bangladesh%20and%20their%20temples%20following%20the%20fall%20of%20the%20Sheikh%20Hasina%20regime%20in%20August.%20This%20turmoil%20brought%20the%2039-year-old%20monk%20into%20the%20public%20eye%20as%20he%20emerged%20as%20a%20key%20figure%20advocating%20for%20the%20rights%20and%20safety%20of%20Hindus%20in%20the%20country.%20In%20just%20a%20few%20months%2C%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20Brahmachari%20has%20become%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prominent%20leaders%20of%20the%20Hindu%20community%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20response%20to%20Brahmachari's%20arrest%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20of%20India%20expressed%20%E2%80%9Cdeep%20concern%E2%80%9D%20over%20the%20court's%20decision%20to%20deny%20him%20bail.%20An%20MEA%20statement%20emphasised%20that%20the%20arrest%20occurred%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20widespread%20violence%20against%20Hindus%20and%20other%20minority%20communities%20in%20Bangladesh.%20The%20MEA%20pointed%20out%20that%20these%20attacks%2C%20including%20arson%2C%20looting%20of%20minority-owned%20properties%2C%20theft%2C%20vandalism%2C%20and%20desecration%20of%20temples%20and%20deities%2C%20have%20continued%20unchecked.%20It%20was%20noted%20that%20despite%20these%20attacks%2C%20religious%20leaders%20like%20Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20Brahmachari%2C%20who%20advocate%20for%20peaceful%20change%2C%20are%20facing%20charges%2C%20while%20the%20perpetrators%20of%20violence%20remain%20unpunished.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732776840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fninval3k_isckon-priest-hindu-priest-chinmoy-krishna-das_625x300_26_November_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fwho-is-chinmoy-krishna-das-brahmachari-the-iskcon-priest-under-arrest-in-bangladesh-7123388%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chinmoy%20Krishna%20Das%20Brahmachari%2C%20an%20ISKCON%20priest%20and%20spokesperson%20for%20the%20Bangladesh%20Sammilita%20Sanatani%20Jagran%20Jote%2C%20was%20arrested%20on%20November%2025%2C%202024%2C%20by%20the%20Dhaka%20Metro