ia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-150x200.jpeg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-1200x1600.jpeg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286-640x853.jpeg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-11-27-at-1.43.39-PM_11zon-1732714286.jpeg%201805w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-383607%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20community%20collaborates%20closely%20with%20the%20Forest%20Department%2C%20sharing%20resources%20and%20assistance%20to%20care%20for%20injured%20animals.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20get%20about%205-7%20calls%20daily%2C%20about%20one%20injured%20animal%20or%20the%20other.%20We%20either%20take%20our%20bikes%20or%20rent%20a%20car%2C%20and%20we%20go%20and%20see%20what%20the%20problem%20is%20and%20take%20the%20animal%20to%20be%20treated%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharvan%20manages%20his%20full%20time%20job%20in%20wildlife%20conservation%20and%20farming%2C%20with%20his%20efforts%20on%20the%20ground.%20%E2%80%9CLuckily%2C%20I%20have%20a%20five-day%20work%20week%2C%20so%20during%20the%20weekends%2C%20I%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20this%20work.%20But%20since%20my%20job%20is%20to%20be%20on%20field%20and%20interact%20with%20the%20farmers%2C%20even%20that%20helps%20me%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20what%20we%20are%20trying%20to%20do%20in%20terms%20of%20conservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20when%20I%E2%80%99m%20not%20there%2C%20other%20people%2C%20especially%20my%20friends%2C%20Jagdish%20and%20Radheshyam%2C%20take%20care%20of%20everything.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWildlife%20conservation%20is%20something%20that%20our%20entire%20community%20is%20committed%20to.%20But%20I%20especially%20feel%20for%20the%20Great%20Indian%20Bustard%2C%20which%20has%20been%20declared%20the%20most%20critically%20endangered%20species%20of%20birds%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2028-year-old%20Radheshyam%20Bishnoi.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20December%2C%20all%20the%20water%20sources%20usually%20dry%20up%2C%20so%20we%20regularly%20refill%2010%2C000-litre%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F352370%2Fsave-birds-in-heatwaves-summer-free-bird-feeders-kapil-prajapat-sirohi-ngo%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewatering%20holes%20to%20help%20bi%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F233508%2Fwater-well-digging-cost-farmers-irrigation-karnataka-professor-digs-open-well-ancestral-village-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erds%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20vultures%2C%20eagles%2C%20and%20bustards%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20deal%20with%20the%20issue%20of%20poaching%2C%20Radheshyam%20has%20formed%20a%20community%20of%20people%20in%20poaching-prone%20areas.%20%E2%80%9CWhenever%20they%20suspect%20any%20illegal%20activity%2C%20they%20contact%20us%2C%20and%20we%20contact%20the%20authorities%20concerned%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%20He%20even%20organises%20birdwatching%20activities%20to%20further%20fund%20his%20conservation%20work.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20three%20of%20us%20have%20full%20time%20jobs.%20What%20we%20wanted%20to%20do%20was%20set%20an%20example%20that%20if%20we%20can%20do%20it%2C%20then%20everyone%20can%20take%20some%20time%20out%20and%20do%20their%20part%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Jagdish.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharvan%E2%80%99s%20community%20has%20become%20an%20integral%20part%20of%20his%20efforts%2C%20with%20people%20from%20surrounding%20areas%20like%20Barmer%2C%20Jaisalmer%2C%20and%20Bikaner%20joining%20the%20cause.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20all%20work%20together%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESharvan%E2%80%99s%20tireless%20efforts%20have%20not%20been%20without%20sacrifice.%20One%20particularly%20harrowing%20day%2C%20a%20farmer%E2%80%99s%20urgent%20call%20led%20him%20to%20a%20heart-wrenching%20sight.%20When%20Sharvan%20arrived%2C%20he%20found%20not%20only%20the%20two%20deer%20trapped%20and%20dead%20but%20also%20the%20heartbreaking%20sight%20of%20another%20deer%20helplessly%20waiting%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20fence.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20deer%20has%20always%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20ecosystem%2C%20coexisting%20with%20the%20farming%20community%20and%20the%20lands%2C%20and%20now%20it%E2%80%99s%20like%20it%20has%20been%20cast%20out%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sharvan%20reflects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20wildlife%20that%20once%20flourished%20around%20them%20is%20disappearing%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20responsibility%20of%20the%20local%20community%20to%20step%20up%20and%20protect%20it.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20does%20not%20matter%20to%20me%20if%20a%20sanctuary%20has%205%2C000%20deer.%20I%20want%20this%20place%2C%20where%20I%20live%2C%20to%20be%20a%20healthy%20ecosystem%20like%20it%20was%20before%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20his%20voice%20filled%20with%20emotion.%20%E2%80%9CMy%20biodiversity%20needs%20its%20own%20plantation%20and%20wildlife%2C%20and%20all%20of%20that%20deserves%20to%20be%20protected.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Arunava%20Banerjee%3B%20All%20Images%20Courtesy%20Sharvan%20Patel%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1732717800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D383592%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Wildlife%20conservationist%20Sharvan%20Patel%20is%20using%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20of%201%2C000%20members%2C%20each%20contributing%20Rs%20365%20annually%2C%20to%20restore%20habitats%2C%20protect%20endangered%20species%2C%20and%20improve%20farming%20practi