that%20payment%20into%20energy%20credits%20for%20the%20user.%20These%20energy%20credits%20are%20linked%20to%20the%20user%E2%80%99s%20utility%20accounts%20to%20offset%20their%20power%20bill%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHow%20does%20SundayGrids%20generate%20revenue%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20make%20a%20margin%20when%20users%20place%20a%20reservation.%20Solar%20developers%20also%20pay%20a%20recurring%20platform%20charge%20for%20listing%20and%20managing%20their%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20user%2C%20the%20advantages%20of%20buying%20into%20a%20SundayGrids%20project%20are%20clear.%20Going%20on%20social%20media%20and%20different%20online%20platforms%2C%20there%20are%20a%20variety%20of%20takes%20on%20the%20system%20they%20have%20built.%20While%20some%20are%20sceptical%20of%20the%20savings%2Freturns%20generated%20by%20buying%20into%20a%20commercial%20solar%20project%2C%20others%20see%20it%20as%20a%20means%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F305500%2Fpradeep-kumar-petwar-haryana-farmer-innovates-solar-on-wheels-trolley-panel-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econtribute%20to%20the%20environment%3C%2Fa%3E%20while%20also%20saving%20on%20their%20power%20bills.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSundayGrids-Project-1732196918.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Thus%20far%2C%20SundayGrids%20claims%20to%20have%20over%20600%20subscribers%20on%20their%20community%20solar%20plants.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSundayGrids-Project-1732196918.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSundayGrids-Project-1732196918-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-med